        been advised of the possibility of such damages.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>No support obligation.</strong> Use of Breaks does not create
        any duty to provide support, fixes, updates, or future versions. New
        versions appear when we feel like shipping them.
      </p>
      <p>
